The paper discusses the integration of human feedback with deep reinforcement learning algorithms, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of reinforcement learning in robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV) is also mentioned. Additionally, the paper discusses the role of human operators in providing feedback, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
